item.title: 【General Music Discussion】Do International versions of Roald Dahl's Matilda The Musical actually exist?
item.description: My question is do offical soundtracks with the dubbed songs exist? I haven't been able to find them to buy anywhere but some versions on youtube are different from the film versions, such as not having background dialouge, is the a place Netflix normally releases them?
item.author: ChraveLover
